on  (  1900–2002 ), who in  1936  became Queen Elizabeth as the wife of King George VI, and after his death in  1952  achieved great public affection as Queen Mother for nearly half a century. Even more influentially, it is the name of her daughter  Queen Elizabeth II  (  b. 1926 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Eliza was born in 1200, in Devon, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Thomas Lucombe I."},"et":{"1200–":"1200–Surnud","1200–1220":"1200–1220","1242–1300":"1242–1300","1200–Female":"1200–Surnud","1300":"1300","1200":"1200","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","Stevenstone, Devon, England":"Stevenstone, Devon, England","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1200–":"1200–Kuollut","1200–1220":"1200–1220","1242–1300":"1242–1300","1200–Female":"1200–Kuollut","1300":"1300","1200":"1200","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","Stevenstone, Devon, England":"Stevenstone, Devon, England","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1200–":"1200–Décédée","1200–1220":"1200–1220","1242–1300":"1242–1300","1200–Female":"1200–Décédée","1300":"1300","1200":"1200","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","Stevenstone, Devon, England":"Stevenstone, Devon, Angleterre","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Eliza est née en 1200, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Thomas Lucombe I."},"de":{"1200–":"1200–Verstorben","1200–1220":"1200–1220","1242–1300":"1242–1300","1200–Female":"1200–Verstorben","1300":"1300","1200":"1200","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","Stevenstone, Devon, England":"Stevenstone, Devon, England","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Eliza wurde 1200 in Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Thomas Lucombe I mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1200–":"1200–Desede","1200–1220":"1200–1220","1242–1300":"1242–1300","1200–Female":"1200–Desede","1300":"1300","1200":"1200","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","Ste